Earlier this month, Jake Gyllenhaal showed off his unexpected vocal talents on the set of his Broadway debut, Sunday in the Park with George . Not one to be upstaged by a fellow Hollywood heartthrob, Ryan Gosling has revealed his own secret skill, piano playing, in a new behind-the-scenes compilation from the set of La La Land , courtesy of Variety . Gosling did all his own performances for the movie, which is up for 14 Oscars at this weekend's Academy Awards (including Best Actor for Gosling), and spent three months—two hours a day for six days a week, to be exact —learning to play.
 Watch him perform the solo from "Start a Fire" and practice on set below.
